<template>
  
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      title: "USER LOGIN",
      user: true,
      root: false
    }
  },
  methods: {
    changeUser() {
      if(this.user === false) {
        this.user = true
        this.root = false
      }
    },
    changeRoot() {
      if(this.root === false) {
        this.user = false
        this.root = true
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
header {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin: 3vh 0;
}
nav a { 
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #2c3e50;}
nav #userRouter.router-link-exact-active { font-weight: bold; color:#7BB3BC; }
nav #rootRouter.router-link-exact-active { font-weight: bold; color: #8FACD7 }
</style>
